{"tid":1222502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］有朋友做地政，佢問我有冇idea 可以將啲物資運岀嚟","createTime":"2019-06-14T12:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T12:50:45.000Z","uid":207166,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d024bbad69466efcb701205427901e8f75747aa2","tid":1222502,"uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"話說琴晚發夢<br />\n夢到朋友嘅朋友係做地政(我朋友冇ac)<br />\n佢話呢幾日清完場之後現場仲有好撚多物資<br />\n引述返我個朋友所講嘅<br />\n現場啲M巾多到夠用一世<br />\n啲安全帽就堆到成座山咁高<br />\n仲有好多唔同物資<br />\n例如N95 Mask 嗰啲<br />\n所以想問咁多位巴絲有冇啲咩idea 可以運到佢岀嚟？"},{"pid":"f43f37e1e3e34f43d769671dd759f4769efc01fc","tid":1222502,"uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:38:08.000Z","msg":"開錯台添，應該開吹水台"},{"pid":"6833bf9d0abcc47ce48d3c04908652a557fde999","tid":1222502,"uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:38:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffb73590b47d66408d3552166be427a74dd2a8b9","tid":1222502,"uid":7380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:38:37.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"7761e6c4f95c5e9ae016a03b365449cf91eb36c1","tid":1222502,"uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:38:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7fc544d32dafa590ae23716df602c70034b7c66a","tid":1222502,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:38:48.000Z","msg":"收左係邊先"},{"pid":"b3b8a9c6dc7f8d892434b494899a261030b08444","tid":1222502,"uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:38:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"295ab0582195bf0c76dbacc476ff95d40ed1c1cb","tid":1222502,"uid":199034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"送去堆填區 然後有人執垃圾"},{"pid":"80c7dbaa20e8d87868e2c36e7e69ccfa3cefb3bd","tid":1222502,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:43:22.000Z","msg":"唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clow